						<div class="postbody">One possible suggestion might be that you might only ever need to swap one PRG bank outside of NMI/IRQ, so you could just always write to $8000 to re-select the bank before returning to the main thread. (CHR banking in NMI/IRQ only, $C000 banking only in NMI for music maybe.)</div>

